<%# start: Temporary message for Columbia ETAS.%>
<div class="covid19-temporary-access">
  <div class="covid19-icon">
    <span class="icon-announce" aria-hidden="true"></span>
  </div>
  <div class="covid19-text">
    <%= link_to "https://library.princeton.edu/news/general/2020-08-24/online-access-millions-books-puls-print-collection-resumes-through" do %>
      <h3>Online Access to Millions of Items via HathiTrust</h3>
    <% end %>
    <p>
    Given the continued need for an increased number of students and faculty researching, teaching, and learning remotely this spring, we are pleased to announce the continuation of the HathiTrust Emergency Temporary Access Service (ETAS) through the spring semester. Through this service, millions of books from our print collection are accessible online.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<%# start: Temporary message for covid.%>
<div class="covid19-temporary-access">
  <div class="covid19-icon">
    <span class="icon-announce" aria-hidden="true"></span>
  </div>
  <div class="covid19-text">
    <%= link_to "https://library.princeton.edu/phased-planning-updates" do %>
      <h3>New Services: Study-Browse Service, Pick-up, and Digitization</h3>
    <% end %>
    <p>
    Continuing for the spring semester, access to Library spaces is available via our <%= link_to "Study-Browse Service", "https://library.princeton.edu/services/study-browse" %>. Firestone and most branch libraries are also continuing to offer pick-up service and performing in-house digitization to fulfill requests. Catalog records for many items will now include a button you can use to request pick-up of circulating items, or digitization of items.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<%# end: Temporary message for covid.%>
